JOHANNESBURG (miningweekly.com) &ndash; Vanadium producer Bushveld Minerals&rsquo; subsidiary Bushveld Vametco Limited (BVL)has paid the outstanding $961 010 in fees and interest due to Barak under an $11-million bridge loan facility. BVL had entered into the bridge loan with Barak to help fund the acquisition of a 78.8% interest in Strategic Minerals Corporation. It had already repaid the loan.